cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically visual relationship recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of linguistic priors, which could place it under cs.CL (Computation and Language). Finally, the paper uses the Visual Genome dataset, which is a multimedia dataset, indicating that it could also fall under cs.MM (Multimedia).
